name: MuscleTown
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: muscle town
des:
Welcome to muscle town. This is a physical activity game where you get points and unlock achievements for completing exercise sets. 
This game only uses body weight exercises which can be done anywhere. 
Whats more there's a leader board where you can see you current ranking among all the muscle town users.
The sets are designed in a way that it will not take more than 15 min of your time to get a good workout done.
the exercises used in the workout routines are jumping jack,bur pees,core twist,squats,punches,hooks,upper cuts,sit ups and push ups.

So, come and become a citizen of the Muscle town and find a fun way to do you workouts in home.
